,"msg":"<blockquote>多唔多人玩long board? 一般係咪都係學左普通板先轉玩long board <br />\n見人玩好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nlongboard多數for dancing/down hill<br />\n基本上無必要學左普通先轉longboard<br />\n因為longboard可以話係偏穩陣嘅板<br />\n初學一樣得"},{"pid":"fa5dd5b84d93c7c33a039f9e88186766cd2b55b2","tid":33260,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"新手留名  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識原地Ollie"},{"pid":"8fb659c129a51ce521098990c1cad2c3cd11dbf8","tid":33260,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手留名  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識原地Ollie</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1 練個陣磨穿左三對鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a76bfc4775e74f62ce524a0e9d7ec9cc56b155a","tid":33260,"uid":21530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"有玩fish sk8 同longboard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開tg grp？"},{"pid":"9dce27d81fc15efa0141466efc132eb5fa2ebbd7","tid":33260,"uid":21530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"本身仲想開post添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有巴絲諗緊玩咩好<br />\n可以睇下<br />\n<br />\nfish <br />\n優點 方便 邊度都踩得 輕身易拎 適合影相打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n缺點 踩街如果踩爛地會震 唔夠快 用tricks好易仆街<br />\n<br />\n建議冇乜時間練tricks又想過下癮既可以玩<br />\n<br />\nskate board 即係花板<br />\n優點 練tricks型撚到仆街 減到肥 <br />\n<br />\n缺點 練tricks要好撚有恆心 一個ollie可能已經要練兩三日<br />\n重 要搵場玩 有啲gov板場on99一定要戴頭盔先入得<br />\n<br />\n建議有時間有心機既人先好玩 唔係擺係度冇撚用<br />\n踩街慢+震到瀨